#: ../../source/unit/catch.rst:2 002cf68eda554dabbcb9a8f690ec2fcc
msgid "Catch Unit"
msgstr "Catch Unit"

#: ../../source/unit/catch.rst:7 c20e1450c2764402a19f4fe6ec5a2bea
msgid ""
"Catch is a gripper that uses a SG92R servo as a power source. The servo "
"uses a PWM signal to drive the gripper gear to rotate and control the "
"gripper for clamping and releasing operations. The structure adopts a "
"design compatible with Lego 8mm round holes. You can combine it with "
"other Lego components to build creative control structures, such as "
"robotic arms, gripper carts, etc."
msgstr ""
"Catch 是一款以 SG92R 舵机作为动力源的夹爪。该舵机使用 PWM 信号驱动夹爪齿轮旋转，从而控制夹爪进行夹持和释放操作。其结构采用兼容 "
"Lego 8 mm 圆孔的设计。你可以将其与其他 Lego 组件组合，搭建富有创意的控制结构，例如机械臂、夹爪小车等。"

